<item>
            <title>[LU-19727] Increased test output logging for edge case failures.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19727</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have seen a few cases of rare test failures that are hard to reproduce locally. The goal of this patch it to add more verbose output to select methods inside test-framework.sh related to shutdown / rebooting of nodes.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;While this proposed fix doesn&apos;t directly fix any of the unique failures or examples given below, it should assist with debugging if they arise again in the future.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

